<h1 className={"openapi__heading"}>DelForbidStreamRule</h1>

<MethodEndpoint method={"get"} path={"/"}></MethodEndpoint>


Deletes the Stream publishing prohibition rule.
<Note title="Rate Limit">All Rooms under the same AppID: 10 times/second.</Note>
<Note title="Note">
  - You can use [Describe Stream publishing prohibition rules](./describe-forbid-stream-rules.mdx) to check whether the corresponding Stream publishing prohibition rule was successfully deleted.
  - If the prohibition rule for the specified Stream ID does not exist, calling this interface will not return an error.
</Note>
